The woman as a homemaker is the pillar of the Family and Society. She is instrumental in
building the right values in character in children and providing a conducive family atmosphere.
Sruti Sreekendra focuses on developing the spiritual evolution of women in the family.  
Towards this regular study of scriptures and Bhajan classes are held. Many of these classes 
are presided by Swamiji himself.Many of Sreekendra members are also Sevaks for Balakendra 
classes. Regular training and orientation sessions are held for enhancing the quality and 
delivery of Balakendra classes
