 <h1 style="font-size:x-large; font-family:'Times New Roman', Times, serif">  
Sruti ShikshaKendra is a forum for Imparting spiritual and vedantic knowledge to all 
elders. This is done for achieving a correct focus on one’s duties and outlook to life
for a peaceful family atmosphere. Swamiji conducts regular classes in various parts of 
Chennai based on our ancient scriptures and Vedas. Nearly 80 individuals are part of 
these  classes. Swamiji also conducts parenting seminars on the art of bringing up 
children. In addition to the above, Swamiji conducts Teachers’ training seminars, which 
are popular in many schools. Further, Swamiji also conducts periodic weeklong Gnana 
Yagnas with specific themes to help people lead peaceful and healthy lives.
